para_trans: Maharashtra Building aA sat regarding constitution of Construction Workers "Local Control Committee" a "Divisional Control Committee" under Construction Workers Welfare Board. - A clean sheet.
Industries, Energy, Labour and Mining Department
Government Decision Number: IBANKA-0825 / P.No.197 / WORKERS-7
Madam Cama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,

Batch: - 1. Government Decision No. IBANKA-0825 / Q. No. 197 / Labour-7, dated 09.09.2025 2. Letter from Secretary & CEO, Maharashtra Building & Other Construction Workers Welfare Board, Mumbai No. J. No. 2035/2025 HARNA-2025 / Q. No.164 / PLAN-2, dated 24.09.2025

As per the Government Decision dated 09.09.2025, it has been approved to constitute a "Local Control Committee" of construction workers under the Board to decide on the applications for registration / renewal / benefit (DBT In Money) received on the Integrated Welfare Board of Construction Workers Management System (IWBMS) as follows.

The serial numbers 1 and 6 of the aforesaid Committee are being amended as follows and shall read as follows: - A. No. (2) of the Legislative Assembly of the State in which the said Committee is situated. The local MLA (Member of Legislative Assembly) is the head of a department. Minister or Minister. The Chairman of the Local Control Committee for Construction Workers, who will be of the rank of Minister of State, will be the person recommended by the Minister / Minister of State concerned.
No. (6) Related Labour Remedies / Assistant Labour Commissioner / Government Labour Officer (Registration Officer) - Member Secretary
